{"tid":27423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手汗腳汗撚入","createTime":"2016-12-07T10:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T14:28:00.000Z","uid":49137,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"085c83c356600dcbb5194085ee6bdb86e8a1b3f4","tid":27423,"uid":49137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"唔知點解由中學畢業完之後，d手汗開始多到好似洗完手咁，就算冇野做都好，對手都會無啦啦出手汗，一緊張小小又出手汗。一諗到要同人呃手又出手汗。總之揸乜係手，果樣野就一定會濕撚晒。除非我個人好累，咁就冇精神緊張自然就冇手汗腳汗。<br />\n可能本身性格問題，我係怕生，唔敢同人眼神交流既毒撚。打扮望落唔似毒撚<br />\n真係好辛苦，怕人地望到我d手汗，我就出得更加多。<br />\n唉。。第時有囡囡都唔知點拖佢隻手<br />\n有冇巴絲打都有呢個煩惱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：打緊呢個po果陣都出緊手汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693218f1f13e75f786cf8ee1955089a2e0ec34f1","tid":27423,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:17:25.000Z","msg":"好蝕底<br />\n識玩但好少拖手"},{"pid":"32837bed11e21c35d1b941e23d2c9f434d8fc4ca","tid":27423,"uid":49137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好蝕底<br />\n識玩但好少拖手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係好撚蝕底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識玩姐係點"},{"pid":"4764678fc5608c6942abd7d73b5ff26748111e08","tid":27423,"uid":53590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"一出世就係咁  真係超唔方便  冇拖過女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過已解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但都係冇女拖"},{"pid":"03655dda6e640adefb37670537adae78f31d60c2","tid":27423,"uid":49137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一出世就係咁  真係超唔方便  冇拖過女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過已解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但都係冇女拖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4849fdb1a72d7a17716e5730c298d854a8e51e2","tid":27423,"uid":2215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"我都係咁"},{"pid":"3ed7d2d395328aa3458148264c8ee87faa973c9a","tid":27423,"uid":53590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一出世就係咁  真係超唔方便  冇拖過女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過已解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但都係冇女拖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇情況，一定work嘅就做手術切左條汗腺定唔知咩，但會可能會有代償出汗就GG，可能會出格拉底/ 背脊/ 其他古怪地方<br />\n<br />\n所以我係冇做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經試過中醫，有少少用，不過一唔睇啲汗就會爆釋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後尾有試過用藥用嘅止汗劑 (好似叫Odaban)，原理類似用保鮮紙包住水喉，問題就係我近乎24小時都有汗，好快會谷爆張保鮮紙，就算未爆谷住谷住都會有種針&quot;吉&quot;感覺  (而且支野長期用都唔平...)<br />\n<br />\n最後我係用一種叫iontophoresis嘅方法，上youtube一search就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以自製可以買現成，想知點整再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論係睇情況揀方法    樓主介唔介意講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79314adcea6fe7168b0f467ae59271fa141d85d","tid":27423,"uid":53590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:21:02.000Z","msg":"戴個頭盔先廢事有人試完唔得屌7我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niontophoresis好似好多人都係減少而唔係100%解決左，我自己就少左七八成啦，同埋同手術一樣都係有代償性出汗，格拉底而家好鬼大汗<br />\n不過好處就係唔對路可以停，手術就一去冇回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b651a57d9162b5a86f9bb6783b2eff4237edaa7","tid":27423,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:38:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戴個頭盔先廢事有人試完唔得屌7我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niontophoresis好似好多人都係減少而唔係100%解決左，我自己就少左七八成啦，同埋同手術一樣都係有代償性出汗，格拉底而家好鬼大汗<br />\n不過好處就係唔對路可以停，手術就一去冇回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打點搞法呢個"},{"pid":"f599f5ba7d671ebdd6e4f096e7a12b57fde712d7","tid":27423,"uid":49137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一出世就係咁  真係超唔方便  冇拖過女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過已解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但都係冇女拖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇情況，一定work嘅就做手術切左條汗腺定唔知咩，但會可能會有代償出汗就GG，可能會出格拉底/ 背脊/ 其他古怪地方<br />\n<br />\n所以我係冇做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經試過中醫，有少少用，不過一唔睇啲汗就會爆釋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後尾有試過用藥用嘅止汗劑 (好似叫Odaban)，原理類似用保鮮紙包住水喉，問題就係我近乎24小時都有汗，好快會谷爆張保鮮紙，就算未爆谷住谷住都會有種針&quot;吉&quot;感覺  (而且支野長期用都唔平...)<br />\n<br />\n最後我係用一種叫iontophoresis嘅方法，上youtube一search就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以自製可以買現成，想知點整再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論係睇情況揀方法    樓主介唔介意講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係一緊張，或者有d興奮，對手都即刻出手汗。諗起隻手要掂野，都會即刻出手汗。有陌生人入左我comfort zone,都會出手汗。姐係例如搭lift有好多人企起我身邊，搭地鐵d人係隔離，我隻手捉住地鐵中間支柱都狂出手汗"},{"pid":"4769875a53f1425595d3cca110fbb99940236505","tid":27423,"uid":55079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣，成日俾d女朋友以為我好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed813997037f8021a1de5707edaa2c25a1605460","tid":27423,"uid":49137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:43:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一出世就係咁  真係超唔方便  冇拖過女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過已解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但都係冇女拖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇情況，一定work嘅就做手術切左條汗腺定唔知咩，但會可能會有代償出汗就GG，可能會出格拉底/ 背脊/ 其他古怪地方<br />\n<br />\n所以我係冇做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經試過中醫，有少少用，不過一唔睇啲汗就會爆釋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後尾有試過用藥用嘅止汗劑 (好似叫Odaban)，原理類似用保鮮紙包住水喉，問題就係我近乎24小時都有汗，好快會谷爆張保鮮紙，就算未爆谷住谷住都會有種針&quot;吉&quot;感覺  (而且支野長期用都唔平...)<br />\n<br />\n最後我係用一種叫iontophoresis嘅方法，上youtube一search就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以自製可以買現成，想知點整再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論係睇情況揀方法    樓主介唔介意講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係一緊張，或者有d興奮，對手都即刻出手汗。諗起隻手要掂野，都會即刻出手汗。有陌生人入左我comfort zone,都會出手汗。姐係例如搭lift有好多人企起我身邊，搭地鐵d人係隔離，我隻手捉住地鐵中間支柱都狂出手汗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得係心理問題，姐係一諗就即刻出手汗"},{"pid":"72febb7b193b886f8de07d32c2bd8b9c214e7d81","tid":27423,"uid":49137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戴個頭盔先廢事有人試完唔得屌7我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niontophoresis好似好多人都係減少而唔係100%解決左，我自己就少左七八成啦，同埋同手術一樣都係有代償性出汗，格拉底而家好鬼大汗<br />\n不過好處就係唔對路可以停，手術就一去冇回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇完youtube d片，整一個/買一個要幾錢？同埋用既頻率係點？一日一次？會唔會有咩副作用咁？<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d9f04f860eb53a536630cdbbe704d43996be92","tid":27423,"uid":44741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"以前讀書一默書成本簿又係濕哂、明明啱都變錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩而家做project用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39f02dbe59f6ce29f0fde69566a0e099c22b7df","tid":27423,"uid":49137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主一樣，成日俾<span style=\"color: red;\">d</span>女朋友以為我好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曲線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都覺得好煩，隻手揸住d野都即刻濕撚晒"},{"pid":"2cd1bdee09b637b2747767aae6cbc858d741161b","tid":27423,"uid":49137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前讀書一默書成本簿又係濕哂、明明啱都變錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩而家做project用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌，係阿！一有exam quiz，隻手壓住張紙個位都濕撚晒，搞到要on99一路吹住自己隻手一路做"},{"pid":"d3de7fe8f5886c40ba2ba0fea2ca921a77c5ed34","tid":27423,"uid":35651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1dbc4bb684a80c9ef5ebbc6b97126e17ae92d90","tid":27423,"uid":53590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戴個頭盔先廢事有人試完唔得屌7我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niontophoresis好似好多人都係減少而唔係100%解決左，我自己就少左七八成啦，同埋同手術一樣都係有代償性出汗，格拉底而家好鬼大汗<br />\n不過好處就係唔對路可以停，手術就一去冇回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇完youtube d片，整一個/買一個要幾錢？同埋用既頻率係點？一日一次？會唔會有咩副作用咁？<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買就唔知了<br />\n整的話好簡單錫紙兜2個樓下百佳幾十蚊一pack<br />\n鱷魚夾鴨記幾蚊一大堆夠你用成世 (可能會生鏽你feel到唔通電就要換)<br />\n電就唔洗跟youtube, 大概9V啦幾多A唔重要反正人體電阻好大電唔死你好似係)，總之買幾舊乾電池駁埋加埋9V啦<br />\n<br />\n用量呢就真係睇你幾嚴重喇<br />\n見巴打你上面講話地鐵扶手會濕曬，應該都算幾濕<br />\n我以前就扶手濕撚曬不過又未滴落去，有一次因事好撚緊張就滴少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你應該大概get到我咩狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比你參考，我大概每日40分鐘，18V電，做左一個月就冇得7788，之後就睇情況啦得閒咪勤力啲去旅行停幾日都冇野之後密翻啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9c32e89eeeb4f7cb7f95223f6aa91b41a388c7","tid":27423,"uid":53590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:11:39.000Z","msg":"講漏左  開頭用9V電係youtube啲人講   <br />\n見過有人拍片用到21V<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己調節啦<br />\n不過一開始唔好玩咁大  未習慣個種輕微觸電感覺會嚇死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於副作用...暫時做左半年未見有...<br />\n自己衡量啦  要付出先有收穫<br />\n之前跳舞同女仔parter真係尷尬到想跳出窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b033beefb5b272cf25a57f4acb4efc463cd62bcd","tid":27423,"uid":57536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"人地一講手汗2隻字 即刻出手汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9b6ad714aa2073582a513ea7cf04041b480e16","tid":27423,"uid":49137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講漏左  開頭用9V電係youtube啲人講   <br />\n見過有人拍片用到21V<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己調節啦<br />\n不過一開始唔好玩咁大  未習慣個種輕微觸電感覺會嚇死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於副作用...暫時做左半年未見有...<br />\n自己衡量啦  要付出先有收穫<br />\n之前跳舞同女仔parter真係尷尬到想跳出窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055734af9db560d02365b088f33ce7af5c6c4de1","tid":27423,"uid":49137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地一講手汗2隻字 即刻出手汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都差唔多，每次入番呢個po都好撚多手汗"},{"pid":"0326f995eb7b4276d6643f396c28fa9a5499e579","tid":27423,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一出世就係咁  真係超唔方便  冇拖過女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過已解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但都係冇女拖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇情況，一定work嘅就做手術切左條汗腺定唔知咩，但會可能會有代償出汗就GG，可能會出格拉底/ 背脊/ 其他古怪地方<br />\n<br />\n所以我係冇做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經試過中醫，有少少用，不過一唔睇啲汗就會爆釋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後尾有試過用藥用嘅止汗劑 (好似叫Odaban)，原理類似用保鮮紙包住水喉，問題就係我近乎24小時都有汗，好快會谷爆張保鮮紙，就算未爆谷住谷住都會有種針&quot;吉&quot;感覺  (而且支野長期用都唔平...)<br />\n<br />\n最後我係用一種叫iontophoresis嘅方法，上youtube一search就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以自製可以買現成，想知點整再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論係睇情況揀方法    樓主介唔介意講多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOdaban 我都有有用<br />\n支野2舊水<br />\n不過真係work, <br />\n用完了, 都唔係咁想再買<br />\n因為有時用完會又痕又痛,<br />\n但真係止到汗"},{"pid":"2ca649a5b23b3287ba9516ded7d40239c7c21f67","tid":27423,"uid":53590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nOdaban 我都有有用<br />\n支野2舊水<br />\n不過真係work, <br />\n用完了, 都唔係咁想再買<br />\n因為有時用完會又痕又痛,<br />\n但真係止到汗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打手汗幾嚴重？<br />\n小弟係會見到水珠  唔知係咪咁所以支野止唔住   定係我唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果得其實我都想用odaban唔洗日日電半個鐘咁煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6481d03f0bb6644dc00c949c38d4bc7a5e1e0fe2","tid":27423,"uid":21408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講漏左  開頭用9V電係youtube啲人講   <br />\n見過有人拍片用到21V<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己調節啦<br />\n不過一開始唔好玩咁大  未習慣個種輕微觸電感覺會嚇死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於副作用...暫時做左半年未見有...<br />\n自己衡量啦  要付出先有收穫<br />\n之前跳舞同女仔parter真係尷尬到想跳出窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己都有做仲用到24V<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能習慣左個感覺覺得冇乜野 不過有倒刺嗰d位真係痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己做左年幾<br />\n一開頭勤力日日做真係可以減到9成<br />\n而家穩定左又懶左一星期2次到都減到7成左右<br />\n總之一feel到汗又多返就做密d就得<br />\n不過問題就係緊張嗰時腳同隔辣底依然出好多汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到唔敢買灰色衫著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}